rows.label: qev065303_MSG0001
rows.name:
Phew! I've finally got a break in the workload.
Suppose I should use this opportunity to take a look
at all the paperwork that's been piling up...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065303_MSG0002
rows.name:
...Hmm? Yes? What is it? Oh, and I ask that you
please keep it briefâ€”I rarely get time to myself,
and would prefer to spend it productively.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065303_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Kent how he would describe himself.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065303_SEL0021
rows.name: Tell Kent that Lyvia wants to meet him.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065303_MSG0003
rows.name:
Me? Er, well, I work in mimeosome repair, for starters.
I'm basically a physician for people such as yourself.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065303_MSG0004
rows.name:
I consider that a serious responsibility and strive to be
worthy of my office.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065303_MSG0005
rows.name:
I also believe that the ideal man is calm and rational at
all times, and always capable of making thoughtful,
well-reasoned decisions.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065303_MSG0006
rows.name:
I confess that these views have made me somewhat...
dull as a candidate for partnership, but one cannot
worry overmuch about such things.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065303_MSG0007
rows.name:
A woman wishes to meet me? She must be quite
sensible. Also unusual. ...Perhaps even mad.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065303_MSG0008
rows.name:
Regardless, such a rare creature is well worth taking
the time to meet.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065303_MSG0009
rows.name:
I thankfully have a bit of time to spare,
so I will go speak with her presently.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065303_MSG0010
rows.name:
Lyvia is quite beautiful. Objectively speaking, that is.
She is empirically attractive.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065303_MSG0011
rows.name:
What seems harder to prove is why such a person
would express an interest in me...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065303_MSG0012
rows.name:
I've never met a woman who listened to my mundane
chatter with such interest before. Perhaps she is only
being kind?[ST:wait ]
